  "label": "Severan Dult",
  "description": "This individual is an animated human corpse, reduced to a gaunt, tendon-bound frame with bronze skin drawn tight across prominent bone. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare that carries no living reflex. Black hair lies in sparse, unkempt clumps over a scalp marked by old abrasions and healed splits. The mouth and jawline show chronic disfigurement from long decay, leaving the teeth and gums partially exposed even at rest.",
